Afshan Azad ( born 12 February , 1988 ) is a British actress . She is best known for playing Padma Patil in the Harry Potter films . She got the part when casting agents visited her school , and after several auditions , was chosen for the part . She auditioned for the role just for the fun of it . She is good friends with Daniel Radcliffe . She currently lives in Manchester . She is a Muslim , and a second - generation Bangladeshi . Afshan and her co - star Shefali Chowdhury became very close after their acting in Goblet of Fire . Nineteen - year - old Afshan is also an A - level student studying Chemistry , Potions , English and media language at Xaverian College and has just taken her AS level exams . 